Query 1 
select (sum(priceEach*quantityOrdered)) as SellingPrice, orderDate from MillionOrders, OrderLineMillion where MillionOrders.orderId = OrderLineMillion.orderId group by orderDate

without indexing 8.83 sec
With indexing: 6.81 sec on orderDate


Query 2 
select (sum((priceEach-buyPrice)*quantityOrdered)) as Profit, orderDate from MillionOrders, Product , OrderLineMillion where Product.productId = OrderLineMillion.productId and OrderLineMillion.orderId = MillionOrders.orderId group by orderDate;

Without indexing 12.5 sec
With indexing : 6.5 sec on orderDate



Query 3

select  avg(quantityOrdered) as AvgQuantityOrdered, Users.customerName from MillionOrders, Users , OrderLineMillion where Users.userId = MillionOrders.userId and OrderLineMillion.orderId = MillionOrders.orderId group by Users.customerName;
Without indexing 19.4 sec
With indexing 10.1 sec on customerName